com.att.aro.model

Class TraceData

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.att.aro.model.TraceData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class TraceData
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Encapsulates the trace data. Contains methods that parse the files in the trace folder, and convert it to Lists of Data Analyzer bean objects.
    See Also:
